<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-5873/jeans.jpg" title="Click and hold to enlarge." style="width:300px;" class="fillpg" alt="jeans.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
